CIDC Data Model

WES analysis combined files

Description: Combined analysis files for the whole WES assay.

Properties

Property Description Data Type
pair_runs < array >
assays.wes_analysis#pair_analysis

Definitions

pair_analysis

Property Description Data Type
normal Sample wise analysis files for the WES assay. assays.wes_assay#sample_analysis
tumor Sample wise analysis files for the WES assay. assays.wes_assay#sample_analysis
run_id An id used for a paired analysis run. < string >
somatic Somatic variant calling output sample files. assays.wes_core#somatic
neoantigen Neoantigen output files. assays.wes_core#neoantigen
copynumber Copy number output files. assays.wes_core#copynumber
purity Purity output files. assays.wes_core#purity
germline Germline variant output sample files. assays.wes_core#germline
clonality Clonality output files. assays.wes_core#clonality
corealignments Core-alignments output files. assays.wes_core#corealignments
report WES pipeline version/commit string. assays.wes_core#report
msisensor MSISensor2 output files. assays.wes_core#msisensor
rna assays.wes_core#rna
